WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.440 align:middle line:90%


00:00:01.440 --> 00:00:04.140 align:middle line:10%
>> People have been using
various forms of energy

00:00:04.140 --> 00:00:08.160 align:middle line:10%
medicine for thousands of
years, yet it has never been

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:11.760 align:middle line:10%
rigorously studied as a
scientifically verifiable form

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:14.370 align:middle line:10%
of healing until now.

00:00:14.370 --> 00:00:16.758 align:middle line:90%
This is "Gaia News."

00:00:16.758 --> 00:00:19.746 align:middle line:90%
